      "hash": "19d7e81b0a8f0769e0c944e48ab29c86d42bac1f",
      "heading": "Custom Insert Molding With Xometry",
      "level": "h3",
      "text": "Custom Insert Molding With Xometry Xometry offers insert mold services as part of its injection molding capabilities . For a free insert molding design review and quote, upload your CAD files . Our expert team of injection molders will get back to you within 24 hours. If you want to learn more about our injection molding capabilities, download our design guideÂ here . If injection molding isnât the best fit for you, you could also tryÂ urethane casting Â orÂ 3D printing . Insert Molding is an injection molding process that works especially well for parts that have threaded holes. It can also help you create better wheels, pulleys, fan blades, and other similar parts. Done correctly, inser..."
    },
